Protecting data and privacy is about taking the necessary steps to prevent personal information from falling into the wrong hands.


Computing devices stores a lot of your personal data. which makes it important to protect the security of our devices.

IoT devices pose greater risk than other computing devices. The best way to protect any IoT devices is to set up on an isolated network.

Make device safe and secure by doing the following:
Turn the firewall on
Set up password protection
Install antivirus and antispyware
Manage your operating system and browser.
